-Am I going to jail?

49:38.901 --> 49:40.858
We have pictures of you...

49:40.986 --> 49:44.236
forcibly restraining a naked young woman
who is crying.

49:44.364 --> 49:46.986
There's probably a crime
in there someplace.

49:47.576 --> 49:50.743
Tell him, Kevin. Was it Bo Marino?

49:53.707 --> 49:56.827
-Do you want to go to jail?
-He'll be pissed at me.

49:59.421 --> 50:00.999
Was it Bo Marino?

50:06.803 --> 50:07.918
Yes.

50:09.807 --> 50:11.051
Who else?

50:15.354 --> 50:16.385
Yes.

50:20.901 --> 50:24.234
-He's never been in trouble before.
-Now he is

50:25.197 --> 50:28.530
-But he's not gonna go to jail, is he?
-Not tonight.

50:29.243 --> 50:34.035
But, Mrs. Feeney, your son participated
in the gang rape of a 16-year-old girl.

50:35.123 --> 50:37.163
He'll have to answer for that.

50:39.461 --> 50:40.243
What else?

50:48.470 --> 50:49.751
through 1990.

50:49.888 --> 50:53.838
They have two cars.
the red Explorer and a black BMW.

50:54.810 --> 50:56.434
How'd you know that?

50:57.146 --> 51:01.190
I'm the police chief. I know everything.
Listen, I have to call you back.

51:05.195 --> 51:06.773
Hold that thought!

51:13.328 --> 51:16.614
-Miss Fiore.
-Save the "Miss" for court.

51:18.292 --> 51:20.000
ls this a house call?

51:21.044 --> 51:24.876
Pour me a drink, would you?
A very large, very dry martini.

51:27.176 --> 51:28.967
-You have kettle One?
-I do.

51:36.101 --> 51:38.141
My plan was for you to be so taken
with me that you'd do whatever I wanted.

51:38.520 --> 51:40.145
lt's working.

51:41.023 --> 51:44.474
That was a lousy way to get
Bo charged with sexual assault.

51:46.236 --> 51:47.481
He deserved it.

51:48.780 --> 51:51.485
I could take you apart in court for that.

51:52.409 --> 51:55.196
But if I did, how would I get you into bed?

52:06.715 --> 52:10.131
-Mostly, I'm thinking 'wow'.
-Good.  I like 'wow'.

52:11.053 --> 52:14.173
ln the small moments,
between thinking "wow"...

52:25.567 --> 52:27.145
Try not to babble.

52:34.743 --> 52:37.151
