52:41.083 --> 52:43.538
You were a homicide detective
in Los Angeles...

52:43.669 --> 52:47.085
but your marriage went south
and you had a drinking problem.

52:47.422 --> 52:49.748
-How's the marriage?
-Still south.

52:50.133 --> 52:52.126
-And the drinking?
-Better.

52:53.470 --> 52:56.804
I also know that
you have a serial killer operating here.

52:58.308 --> 53:00.978
-You must be stretched pretty thin.
-We are.

53:01.103 --> 53:04.057
But you still had time
to run down this rape thing.

53:05.274 --> 53:08.061
Usually, you get into
one of these small, suburban towns...

53:08.193 --> 53:11.776
they have a homicide,
and the State Police take over pretty quickly.

53:11.905 --> 53:14.527
We try to handle as much
as we can in-house.

53:30.257 --> 53:31.585
Buy me dinner!

53:32.843 --> 53:34.218
I'll dress up.

53:35.012 --> 53:37.004
Fluff up my body a little.

53:37.764 --> 53:38.879
Wow.

53:46.148 --> 53:49.268
I know how much pressure
you must be under now...

53:55.157 --> 53:59.368
But we agreed that
if we blew the whistle and corroborated...

53:59.495 --> 54:03.872
we might not get them, and that would
make her life very difficult in Paradise.

54:04.875 --> 54:07.033
They were gonna show my picture
to everyone.

54:07.169 --> 54:09.126
Now they probably won't.

54:12.716 --> 54:15.634
I'll give a statement.
I'll testify, if I have to.

54:19.515 --> 54:21.840
