-You can't go in.

54:21.975 --> 54:24.513
This is all bullshit. Kevin Feeney lied.

54:24.645 --> 54:27.314
-I'm sorry, Skipper.
-lt's all right, Tony.

54:27.648 --> 54:29.475
Close the door behind you.

54:32.194 --> 54:34.352
My kid told you he didn't threaten her.

54:34.488 --> 54:38.486
He told her that if she testified
against him, he'd kill her...

54:38.617 --> 54:40.657
Come on, it's just his
word against hers.

54:40.786 --> 54:44.071
